{"arkId":"cl010064458","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010064458","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Le Triomphe de saint Thomas d\u0027Aquin","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Le Triomphe de saint Thomas d\u0027Aquin"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 3e quart du XVe si\u00e8cle (1450 - 1475)","currentLocation":"Denon, [Peint] Salle 708 - Salon Carr\u00e9","room":"Salle 708, Aile Aile Denon, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1450,"endYear":1475,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Gozzoli, Benozzo (Benozzo di Lese di Sandro, dit)","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1497","place":"Pistoie","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1420","place":"Florence","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q248615"},{"label":"Italie Toscane Florence","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"\u00c9cole de","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"INV 104","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"MR 255","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Peintures","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"A la partie sup\u00e9rieure le Christ b\u00e9nissant dans une gloire entre saint Paul, Mo\u00efse et les quatre \u00c9vang\u00e9listes ; au registre m\u00e9dian, saint Thomas d\u0027Aquin encadr\u00e9 d\u0027Aristote et de Platon, terrassant Averro\u00e8s ; \u00e0 la partie inf\u00e9rieure, une assembl\u00e9e d\u0027ecl\u00e9siastiques et de la\u00efcs pr\u00e9sid\u00e9e par un pape (Pie II selon Guerini qui voit dans cette sc\u00e8ne la dispute sur le sang du Christ tenue au Palais apostolique en 1463).","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ;  (Armoiries non identifi\u00e9es sur la partie inf\u00e9rieure gauche du repeuint. Nombreuses inscriptions en capitales donnant l\u2019identit\u00e9 de certains personnages et explicitant leurs rapports avec saint Thomas (relev\u00e9 dans Guerrini, 1989, \u00e9d. 1993).)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,3","displayDimension":"2,3 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1,02","displayDimension":"1,02 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"tempera (?) sur bois (peuplier)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Cath\u00e9drale de Pise, derri\u00e8re le si\u00e8ge de l\u0027archev\u00eaque (cit\u00e9 en 1568 par Vasari, puis en 1605) ; emplacement identique jusqu\u0027en novembre 1812 selon l\u0027argumentation s\u00e9duisante de Guerrini (pour d\u0027autres auteurs, fix\u00e9 \u00e0 un pilier de la nef ou de la coupole \u00e0 partir de 1630) ; pr\u00e9lev\u00e9 et emport\u00e9 au Louvre, 1813.\r\nLe panneau a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9coup\u00e9 en cintre \u00e0 la partie sup\u00e9rieure et repeint de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 sur le bord nu, vraisemblablement au XVIe si\u00e8cle. Armoiries non identifi\u00e9es sur la partie inf\u00e9rieure gauche du repeint. Nombreuses inscriptions en capitales donnant l\u2019identit\u00e9 de certains personnages et explicitant leurs rapports avec saint Thomas (relev\u00e9 dans Guerrini 1993).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"conqu\u00eate militaire","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1813","startYear":1813,"endYear":1813}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Pei